headline: Extra Space Storage Inc. Announces 4th Quarter 2025 Dividend
summary: Extra Space Storage Inc. (the "Company") (NYSE: EXR) announced today that the Company's board of directors has declared a fourth quarter 2025 dividend of $1.62 per share on the common stock of the Company. The dividend is payable on December 31, 2025, to stockholders of record at the close of business on December 15, 2025.

headline: Self-storage real estate has ‘close to zero’ correlation to the broader economy. That's a good thing
summary: Over the last 15 years, self-storage has outperformed industrial, multifamily, office and retail in net operating income, according to a new Heitman report.
